'''''Fallen Petals, Leave Fading Traces of Fragrance''''' is a [[Trailblaze Mission]] in the chapter [[As Tomorrow Became Yesterday]].

==Steps==
# Depart from the eternal page to embark on a journey to look back into the past
# Cast ripples and bid the final farewell
# Anchor the original causality with the ceremonial blade
# Find a warm and familiar place to get some proper rest
# Cast ripples and initiate the first gaze backward
# Cast ripples and initiate the second gaze backward
# Cast ripples and initiate the third gaze backward
# Cast ripples and initiate the fourth gaze backward
# Cast ripples and initiate the fifth gaze backward
# Return to the girl's homeland
# Entrust the prophecy to the villagers

